    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Extinct family containing four genera and five species from Madagascar, all extinct within the past 2,000 years. Developed in the Holocene. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
